title: I can't transfer my account to other places
body:
Just left.my.country. Missed it alot
want to play LoL again. nut i cant transfer.my.acc. 



please.let us transfer.our accs to garena

replies.body: I wish we could help with this, but NA support isn't able to manually perform transfers to Garena.  We also have no jurisdiction over at the region, so you'll have to reach out to [Garena Support](http://support.lol.garena.com/en_SG) directly to see if there's anything they can do.  I wish you the best of luck with this!
Please let.eiot see this and make us immigrants play wih our pals from our places back home
